description.en: With all the recent mania, greed and copycat projects, we decided to launch a wholesome coin dedicated to those women who brought us into the world: our moms. Enter MILF (Moms I'd Like to Fund). The goal of the project is to build a strong, wholesome community centered around charity towards those moms that need a little extra. To that end, we are organising donation drives to selected mom-related charities and trying to give back to the world.
